		- |ERR_NO_RECIPE_MANAGER_SET|
		- |ERR_OK|

 See :ref:`ReturnValues` for a description of all possible errors.
]]></Comment><ReturnType>DWORD</ReturnType><ReturnBitSize>32</ReturnBitSize><Parameter><Name>RecipeDefinitionName</Name><Comment><![CDATA[	Name of the recipe definition ]]></Comment><Type>STRING(80)</Type><BitSize>648</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>RecipeName</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Name of the recipe ]]></Comment><Type>STRING(80)</Type><BitSize>648</BitSize></Parameter></Method><Method><Name>SaveRecipe</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Stores the recipe into the standard recipe file

